					<div class="subject">
		<h5>United States History</h5>
		<ul>
						<li>
				<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>31</strong>&nbsp;<span>Understands economic, social, and cultural developments in the contemporary United States.</span></p>
			</li>
					</ul>
	</div>
</div>
</div>
